Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Being 'on welfare'
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf3d
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Oct 1984
Confused messages about poverty levels in the US come from media reports misinterpreting the official figures. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less